org.finra.herd.service.helper

Class EmrStepHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.finra.herd.service.helper.EmrStepHelper
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmrHadoopJarStepHelper, EmrHiveStepHelper, EmrPigStepHelper, EmrShellStepHelper

    public abstract class EmrStepHelper
extends Object
    Base abstract class for EMR step helpers. All EMR step helpers will extend this class.
